parts:
{
  "prompt": "Anime-style illustration of the main characters from Stranger Things Season 3, including Eleven, Mike, Dustin, Lucas, Will, Max, Steve, and Robin, standing together in a dramatic pose with supernatural lighting and retro 1980s background. Each character should have distinct anime features like expressive eyes and stylized outfits, but still be recognizable.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A richly textured illustration of characters from the Malazan Book of the Fallen reimagined in Appalachian folk art style. The scene shows a weathered warrior (like Whiskeyjack) in hand-stitched clothes standing near a foggy mountain ridge, with symbols of magic and ancient grief carved into a tree behind him. A hooded sorcerer figure watches from the cabin porch, and spectral wolves drift through a twilight hollow. The palette is muted earth tones with touches of mystical blue. The landscape features rough-hewn cabins, overgrown paths, and distant storm clouds.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A dark, moody illustration of a tall, brooding warrior resembling a T'lan Imass (undead, stone-faced, ancient) standing in a modern Appalachian trailer park at dusk. The trailer park is quiet and slightly rundown, with mist rolling in from the hills. The warrior wears ancient armor covered in dust and bone fragments, contrasting starkly with the aluminum siding and satellite dishes of the trailers. He holds a stone sword, its tip resting on the gravel, and stares silently across the trailers as if remembering an ancient war. The scene is cinematic, blending fantasy and realism, with a melancholic, mythic tone.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A dark fantasy painting of a skeletal undead warrior with a bare skull for a head, standing in a run-down Appalachian trailer park under a cloudy sky. The figure wears tattered, worm-eaten leather armor with a single shoulder pauldron, worn greaves, and gauntlets. His eyes glow faintly within the skull. In his hand, he carries a massive, ancient bone blade. The scene is moody, misty, and grounded in realism, blending grim high fantasy with rural American decay.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A dramatic painting in the style of The Last Supper, featuring the Hellfire Club from Stranger Things playing Dungeons & Dragons. Eddie Munson is in the central position, styled as Jesus, wearing a long robe with the Hellfire Club logo. The other members are seated around the table in similar medieval-inspired robes with subtle Hellfire insignias. The scene is lit with moody, cinematic lighting, and the setting resembles a blend of a church hall and a fantasy-themed D&D lair. Rich detail, somber atmosphere, and reverent composition.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A 1980s-style neon digital painting featuring a roaring American muscle car (such as a Dodge Charger or Pontiac GTO) barreling forward on a glowing synthwave highway, surrounded by glowing palm trees and mountains, under a dark purple and magenta sky. The car is powerful and raw, clearly not built for drifting—only forward motion. Above the scene, in bold, stylized retro-futuristic 80s font, the caption reads: 'ALL FIRE NO DRIFT'. The overall aesthetic should channel vaporwave and synthwave styles, with glowing gridlines on the road and dramatic lighting from neon signs.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A dramatic Viking funeral scene set in a misty Appalachian holler. A small wooden funeral boat floats gently down a narrow river that carved the hollow over centuries. Flames rise from the pyre on the boat, illuminating the forested cliffs on either side. At the heart of the fire, a glowing three-bar Orthodox cross burns brightly, half-consumed by flame, half-radiant. The river glows with reflections of fire and fog, and a few shadowed figures stand silently on the rocky shore, watching the vessel pass through. The mood is somber, sacred, and mythic.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
